        <section class="overview">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>The MinSU Student Management System (SMS) is designed to efficiently manage student information, streamline administrative tasks, and enhance the overall educational experience.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="objectives">
            <h2>Objectives</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date student records.</li>
                <li>Facilitate easy access to student information for administrators and faculty.</li>
                <li>Improve the efficiency of student-related processes and operations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section class="vision">
            <h2>Vision</h2>
            <p>To be the leading student management system that empowers educational institutions with innovative and user-friendly solutions for managing student data.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="mission">
            <h2>Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide a comprehensive, reliable, and scalable student management system that supports the administrative and academic needs of educational institutions, ensuring a seamless experience for all users.</p>
        </section>
